{"tid":2055851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐「冤枉監」72天 大學生患焦慮症 眾籌入稟向警索償 帳戶遇襲92萬被凍","createTime":"2020-06-08T09:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:48:06.000Z","uid":53379,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc87fdb92c37833abe288dc6fc147e5cc75365b","tid":2055851,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">坐「冤枉監」72天 大學生患焦慮症 眾籌入稟向警索償 帳戶遇襲92萬被凍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】在荔枝角收押所度過72日後，大學生J（化名）身形增大了一圈，穿不上之前買的西裝外套。他去年11月捲入一宗丫叉郵包案，今年2月獲撤控，兩個多月的「冤枉監」令他患上焦慮症，因藥物副作用發胖。他原打算眾籌提出民事索償，追究警方有否濫控，但帳戶遭惡意攻擊，目前籌得的逾92萬元被凍結，「可能我行衰運，希望最後都能討回公道吧」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200608/s00001/1591554570682/%E5%9D%90%E3%80%8C%E5%86%A4%E6%9E%89%E7%9B%A3%E3%80%8D72%E5%A4%A9-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%82%A3%E7%84%A6%E6%85%AE%E7%97%87-%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E5%B8%B3%E6%88%B6%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B292%E8%90%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%87%8D?fbclid=IwAR0llbG5fcnaQ46vLggiURA6vA1V_ryBdkLdmm0_s9hs6BKXm9AiRqzhWIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200608%2Fs00001%2F1591554570682%2F%25E5%259D%2590%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2586%25A4%25E6%259E%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E3%2580%258D72%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%2584%25A6%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%2597%2587-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B292%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2587%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0llbG5fcnaQ46vLggiURA6vA1V_ryBdkLdmm0_s9hs6BKXm9AiRqzhWIU&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=f999f4d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200608%2Fs0000